result:
<v-flex xs12 sm6 md4 d-flex>
  <v-select
    :items="anos"
    label="Ano de Fabricação"
    outline
    color="teal darken-2"
    v-model="ano"
    append-icon="fas fa-calendar-check"
    @change="Selecionar(ano)"
    :rules="[() => !!ano || 'Este campo precisa ser selecionado!']"
  >
    <template slot="item" slot-scope="data">
      <v-flex xs10 sm10>
        <v-list-tile>
          <v-list-tile-content>
            <v-list-tile-title>{{data.item}}</v-list-tile-title>
          </v-list-tile-content>
        </v-list-tile>
      </v-flex>
      <v-flex xs2 sm2>
        <v-btn flat icon color="red lighten-1 " @click="DeletarAno(data.item.id)">
          <v-icon>fas fa-trash-alt</v-icon>
        </v-btn>
      </v-flex>
    </template>
  </v-select>
  <cad-ano v-on:anos="AtualizarAnos"></cad-ano>
</v-flex>
